data.description: Welcome to 910 Spencer Dr.  This is the perfect home for the 1st Time Buyer or Downsizing. As you walk into the Living Room/Dining Room notice the Ceramic Tile floor which leads to the Remodeled Eat in Kitchen with Wood Cabinets, Stainless Steel Dishwasher. The Kitchen leads to the Spacious Addition of a 2nd Family/Living Room with a Brick Fireplace. The Sliding Door from the Family Room goes out to a Large Covered Deck with a Snack Bar. Perfect for Relaxing and Enjoying the Outdoors in your Fenced in Yard. Also included are 2 Storage Sheds. 3 Bedrooms and a Full Updated Bath and all Rooms have Crown Molding and Ceiling Fans. Don't bypass this Opportunity to Own a Home that has Features for Relaxing, Entertaining and Outdoor Enjoyment. Easy access to Train, 95 Rt1, Shopping, Entertainment and Neshaminy Park and Marina.  Through a Trusted Lender this Qualifies for the Community Lending Advantage Mortgage Discount Program. This home qualifies for a Rate REDUCTION!! House is being sold "as is". Buyer is Responsible for U & O.
